      "input": "str | mote",
      "output": "[mote]",
      "text": "返回一个列表，包含当前绑定的枢纽中所有对应于指定类型的物元。"
    },
    {
      "type": "hexcasting:pattern",
      "op_id": "hexal:mote/make",
      "anchor": "hexal:mote/make",
      "input": "(item) | (item, mote)",
      "output": "mote",
      "text": "将一份物品实体转换为物元，并存入绑定的枢纽中。若同时传入一个物元，则会将所给物体与该物元合并，消耗 10 点媒质。"
    },
    {
      "type": "hexcasting:pattern",
      "op_id": "hexal:mote/return",
      "anchor": "hexal:mote/return",
      "input": "(mote, vec) | (mote, vec, num)",
      "output": "",
      "text": "将一个物元转换为物品实体，并生成于指定坐标向量。若同时传入一个数，则最多返还指定数量，消耗 100 点媒质。"
    },
    {
      "type": "hexcasting:pattern",
      "header": "hexcasting.action.hexal:mote/combine",
      "op_id": "hexcasting:add",
      "anchor": "hexal:mote/combine",
      "input": "mote, mote",
      "output": "mote",
      "text": "将第二条物元合并至第一条物元中。"
    },
    {
